            <characteristic name="Abilities" typeId="d93f-70ee-72bc-5ef9">Suppressive (3D3), For each attack made for this weapon that targets a vehicle unit, the Strength of that attack is improved to 16. If that wound roll is successful, after the Attacks step, the target unit must make an Explode Roll.</characteristic>
