            <profile name="Immaculate Choreography" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="71d5-b598-ee4e-1c0d">
              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit&apos;s Move step, you may select any other LIGHT TROUPE, DARK TROUPE or TWILIGHT TROUPE unit which is not ready, is visible to this unit and has not been selected for any Immaculate Choreography this battle round. If you do, until the End step, this unit gains the following abilities:


Awaiting Cue: After this unit gains this ability, you may have this unit become ready. If you do, skip the Attacks step.


Carnage Bloom: For each attack made for this unit, reroll a Hit Roll of 1 for that attack.</characteristic>
              </characteristics>
            </profile>
          </profiles>
          <constraints>
